      "If you want to make transactions using the Lightning Network, you’ll need to send some BTC (for instance from your Ai Earn account) to a Lightning-compatible wallet. There are dozens to choose from. Popular options include both \"custodial\" and \"non-custodial\" wallets. Here’s the difference: ",
