      "Advanced Trade fees",
      "Ai Earn uses a maker-taker fee model for determining advanced trading fees. Orders that provide liquidity (maker orders) are charged different fees than orders that take liquidity (taker orders). Fees are calculated based on the current pricing tier you are in when the order is placed, and not on the tier you would be in after a trade is completed. You can check your",
