      "DeFi Investment Risks",
      " Disclaimer: Ai Earn is not an investment advisor. This article is for informational purposes only and is not financial advice. Please do your own research and consult a financial advisor before making any investment decisions. ",
      "DeFi investments have seven main risk categories: ",
