      "If you would like to obtain liquidity on your staked ETH sooner, you have the option to wrap your Ai Earn staked ETH for cbETH until the Shanghai upgrade is complete. Note that the price of cbETH is determined by the market. To learn more about cbETH please visit our help center article - using cbeth.",
